index_terms: CHICAGO MILWAUKEE ST. PAUL PACIFIC RAILROAD
summary: An ordinance relating to the Water Dept. and approving a conveyance, quitclaim and release between the Chicago, Milwaukee, St. Paul and Pacific Railroad Company, Mountain Development Company and Weyerhaeuser Company, in connection with certain property in Sections 23 & 24, Township 22 North, Range 6 East, W.M.
